(42, 21, 22, 23, 63, 4, 4, 'the days of vengeance', 'Connection of Vengeance Themes', 'Both passages emphasize the concept of vengeance, indicating a significant moment in divine judgment. Luke refers to ''the days of vengeance,'' while Isaiah speaks of ''the day of vengeance,'' highlighting a shared theme of divine retribution.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 21, 22, 61, 2, 9, 9, 'the days of vengeance', 'Connection of Judgment and Deliverance', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of divine judgment and deliverance. Luke 21:22 speaks of the days of vengeance, while 2 Peter 2:9 mentions the day of judgment for the unjust, highlighting God''s ability to deliver the godly.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 21, 22, 24, 51, 6, 6, 'these be the days of vengeance', 'Days of Vengeance Connection', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of vengeance from the Lord. Luke 21:22 refers to ''the days of vengeance,'' while Jeremiah 51:6 speaks of ''the time of the Lord’s vengeance.'' This connection highlights the fulfillment of divine judgment.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
