(42, 21, 23, 41, 13, 17, 17, NULL, 'Connection of Woe for Mothers', 'Both passages emphasize the distress faced by those with children during difficult times. The repetition of the phrase about those ''with child'' and ''give suck'' highlights a shared concern in both texts.', 'parallel', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 21, 23, 42, 23, 29, 29, NULL, 'Connection of Distress and Barren', 'This connection highlights the contrasting views on childbearing during times of distress. The first passage warns of woe for those with children, while the second passage speaks of blessings for the barren, suggesting a thematic link between suffering and motherhood.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
